title: Please DON'T Trust Worldcoin...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the world of privacy and how one company is giving away a tiny sum of money to gather the personal data of millions around the world. Biometrics should be considered incredibly private and handing them out to just any company shouldn't be a consideration for many. Why? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
